# UTI Subtypes for Data Detector Types

These constants represent sub-Uniform Type Identifier of `com.apple.structured-text`

## Overview

These constants represent sub-[https://developer.apple.com/library/archive/documentation/General/Conceptual/DevPedia-CocoaCore/UniformTypeIdentifier.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/TP40008195-CH60] of `com.apple.structured-text`, which conforms to `public.plain-text`. Use these constants to specify the type of data your extension works with.

## Constants

- **NSTypeIdentifierDateText**
- **NSTypeIdentifierAddressText**
- **NSTypeIdentifierPhoneNumberText**
- **NSTypeIdentifierTransitInformationText**

## Constants

- **Property Keys**: These keys correspond to the extension item properties and are specified in the extension’s `Info.plist`.
